flowchart TD
    A[Unclear situation] --> B{Can you name the hidden state?}
    B -- no --> B1[Define the relevant state first]
    B -- yes --> C{Is the target fixed or locally fixed?}

    C -- no --> C1[Separate target-occurrence uncertainty from position/state uncertainty]
    C -- yes --> D{Can action affect observation, belief, decision, or state?}

    D -- no --> D1[External uncertainty or outside actionable core]
    D -- yes --> E{Is the observation state-informative?}

    E -- no --> E1[Not a valid re-anchor]
    E -- yes --> F{Can observation change the next action?}

    F -- no --> F1[Weak decision value]
    F -- yes --> G{Does value exceed cost?}

    G -- no --> G1[Valid but unfavorable]
    G -- yes --> H[Favorable action or observation]

    H --> I{Is this repeated observation?}
    I -- yes --> J{MOV_i > 0?}
    J -- no --> J1[Checking loop]
    J -- yes --> K[Continue or choose next observation]
    I -- no --> K

    K --> L{Are you expanding scope?}
    L -- no --> L1[Act within current scope]
    L -- yes --> M{Expansion value exceeds costs and boundary risk?}

    M -- no --> M1[Reduce expansion or observe sooner]
    M -- yes --> N[Expand scope]

    N --> O{Is conclusion kept local?}
    M1 --> O
    L1 --> O

    O -- no --> O1[Local-to-global overreach]
    O -- yes --> O2[Acceptable scoped conclusion]
